born: september 07, 1956 died: june 14, 2015 charles p. chuck graffis i, age, 58, formerly of williamsport, passed away on june 14, 2015, surrounded by his family.
chuck was born on september 7, 1956 in lincoln, nebraska.

he is survived by the love of his life, chris graffis; two daughters, nicole( kerry) larkins and kim graffis; son charles (jenn) graffis; mother, sue graffis; brother, john graffis; and sister teresa (grady) campbell.
chuck also leaves behind an aunt, joyce alkire, 2 nieces, 3 nephews, and 7 great nieces.
he is preceded in death by his father, john graffis, sr.

family will greet friends from 6-8pm on wednesday, june 17, 2015 at porter tidd funeral home, 331 w. main st, mount sterling, oh. a funeral service will be held on thursday, june 18, 2015 at 10am, also at the funeral home.
burial to follow at waterloo cemetery.
